 (IT Asset Management Policy),
 consistent with CJIS Security Policy v6.0:
 Section CM-2(2) (Automation Support for Accuracy and Currency).
 The Assistant IT Director shall configure automated monitoring to generate a work order upon detection of a deviation.
 The responsible Systems Administrator or Network Administrator shall classify the deviation work order at the severity produced by the standard priority calculation,
 and shall remediate the deviation within the response and resolution timeframes defined in 
